{"title":"Launch","type":"markdown","aggs":[],"params":{"fontSize":12,"openLinksInNewTab":false,"markdown":"| Component                                                                                                                                              | Type         | Description                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                         | Launch Options                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   |
|--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|--------------|-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|
| [Hosts](kibana#/dashboard/6ff38e70-a907-11eb-95b4-cb8fe89a1fee)                                                                                        | Dashboard    | Information from the perspective of hosts on the network.  Events and alerts are aggregated over a `24 hour` time period to record  statistical information for hosts. Host definitions are refreshed `every 10 minutes`.   This dashboard provides the ability to *drilldown* into alerts and connections associated with a host. Hosts within this view can easily be filtered by whether they are internal or external to the monitored network. |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  |
| [Alerts](kibana#/dashboard/f227ec60-a907-11eb-95b4-cb8fe89a1fee)                                                                                       | Dashboard    | Traditional IDS (EmergingThreats) alerts show up here.  This dashboard provides the ability to *pivot* to corresponding connections and underlying protocols.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  |
| [Connections](kibana#/dashboard/9fcc14c0-a2e3-11eb-b7a2-7f7bf4b19d40)                                                                                  | Dashboard    | Conversations between hosts show up here. This view is primarily concerned with transport layer details of a connection. Connections can be associated with one or more protocol logs or alerts.  This dashboard provides the ability to *pivot* from a connection into its underlying protocols (if one was detected and parsed).                                                                                                                  |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  |
| [Protocols](kibana#/dashboard/7d11a3a0-8b73-11eb-9b4a-033d9adb6205)                                                                                    | Dashboard    | Application protocol specifics for conversations between hosts. This view is primarily concerned with providing additional details to `connections` where a protocol was detected.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  |
| [Internal Hosts](kibana#/discover/37659f60-ae22-11eb-aebc-5d7e6f8bf146?_g=(time:(from:now-15m,mode:quick,to:now),timeRestore:!f)&_a=())                | Saved Search | Tabular view of internal hosts seen over the last 24 hours.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                         |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  |
| [External Hosts](kibana#/discover/2e546a10-ae21-11eb-aebc-5d7e6f8bf146?_g=(time:(from:now-15m,mode:quick,to:now),timeRestore:!f)&_a=())                | Saved Search | Tabular view of external hosts seen over the last 24 hours.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                         |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  |
